title: Elasticsearch: Cluster Health
agents: elasticsearch
catalog: app/elasticsearch
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the state of an elasticsearch cluster.
 Possible elasticsearch states: green (OK), yellow(WARN), red(CRIT)

 It also shows informations about the cluster name, nodes (count)
 and data nodes (count).

inventory:
 One service is created.

